title: NFL Draft chatter: The Philosophy of the Draft
description: More conversation 92Noon from PA & Nordo, on how the Vikings will be approaching the NFL Draft. Identifying specific players will eventually come, but narrowing down the mindset and direction the team should/will go is the A-Topic.
